import React from 'react'
import {
  Card,
  FormControl,
  FormLabel,
  FormErrorMessage,
  FormHelperText,
  Heading,
  Input,
  InputGroup,
  InputLeftElement,
  NumberInput,
  NumberInputField,
  NumberInputStepper,
  NumberIncrementStepper,
  NumberDecrementStepper,
  Select,
  Textarea
} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const EarningsForm = () => {
  return(
    <Card p={2}>
      <FormControl isRequired>
        <Heading size='md' as='h2'>Earnings Form.</Heading>
        <FormLabel>Entity</FormLabel>
          <Select placeholder='Select Entity'>
            <option>Alice</option>
            <option>Damaris</option>
            <option>Joanna</option>
          </Select>
          <FormLabel>Describe the earnings.</FormLabel>
          <Textarea placeholder='Add context of the event. (Ex...)Think of any new possible leads.' />
      </FormControl>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default EarningsForm
